288
00:22:15,439 --> 00:22:17,259
I'm coming.

289
00:22:28,179 --> 00:22:30,599
- Let me stay at your place for a while. 
 - Hey, shoes.

290
00:22:30,599 --> 00:22:32,939
I'm too tired to change them.

291
00:22:33,919 --> 00:22:35,819
What's wrong?

292
00:22:36,659 --> 00:22:40,839
He Xindi keeps nagging me at home.

293
00:22:40,839 --> 00:22:43,719
She's so annoying, even more than my mom.

294
00:22:43,719 --> 00:22:47,759
She said I got myself a scammer and sent me lots of scam cases she found online.

295
00:22:47,759 --> 00:22:51,419
Is it possible she's hit menopause early or something?

296
00:22:51,419 --> 00:22:53,419
It's about the girl you just met?

297
00:22:53,419 --> 00:22:55,479
We are just communicating normally.

298
00:22:55,479 --> 00:22:58,360
She's introduced by a friend and she's a good person. We're having pretty good chats.

299
00:22:58,360 --> 00:23:02,439
But I didn't say we were going to date. What's Xindi's problem?

300
00:23:02,439 --> 00:23:05,979
Does He Xindi have a thing for you?

301
00:23:05,979 --> 00:23:09,719
Right, she likes to mess with me.

302
00:23:09,719 --> 00:23:13,519
She's so anxious because you're chatting with that girl. Isn't that just jealousy?

303
00:23:13,519 --> 00:23:17,419
Jealousy? She just wants to see my downfall.

304
00:23:17,419 --> 00:23:19,579
Didn't she get cheated on by Chen Xuan before?

305
00:23:19,579 --> 00:23:21,659
I made fun of her. You remember, right?

306
00:23:21,659 --> 00:23:23,999
So she held a grudge, wanting revenge.

307
00:23:23,999 --> 00:23:26,999
She'd love nothing more than to see me swindled by a woman.

308
00:23:26,999 --> 00:23:29,599
That would make her over the moon.

309
00:23:30,619 --> 00:23:32,839
I don't think so.

310
00:23:32,839 --> 00:23:35,279
Do you know her better than I do?

311
00:23:35,279 --> 00:23:37,619
She can't find a boyfriend so she hassles me every day.

312
00:23:37,619 --> 00:23:40,979
Talk about bad luck for me to co-rent and partner up with her.

313
00:23:40,979 --> 00:23:44,499
Staying together 24 hours a day. I can't return anymore.

314
00:23:44,499 --> 00:23:48,539
Tonight I'll stay at your place. Xiao Que won't come, right?

315
00:23:52,279 --> 00:23:54,260
No.

316
00:23:54,260 --> 00:23:57,340
You two haven't made up yet?

317
00:24:01,819 --> 00:24:03,599
Is it that serious?

318
00:24:03,599 --> 00:24:07,919
After being together for so long, you still hold grudges from a fight?

319
00:24:07,919 --> 00:24:10,819
I've also been pretty busy these past few days.

320
00:24:10,819 --> 00:24:14,439
Yes, I know you're busy, but you can't ignore your girlfriend.

321
00:24:14,439 --> 00:24:15,719
You cheat on her?

322
00:24:15,719 --> 00:24:18,759
- What are you talking about? Is it possible? 
 - Then you shouldn't be doing this.

323
00:24:18,759 --> 00:24:21,119
Still giving the silent treatment? We're adults now.

324
00:24:21,119 --> 00:24:25,339
Do you have any idea how many girls end up in someone else's arms because of their boyfriends' silent treatment?

325
00:24:25,339 --> 00:24:27,199
Impossible.

326
00:24:27,199 --> 00:24:31,439
If you're so confident, go ahead and keep up the silent treatment. You might as well break up with her.

327
00:24:31,439 --> 00:24:35,559
- Start dating new ones. I've got a party today with girls. Want to join? 
 - Are you crazy?

328
00:24:35,559 --> 00:24:37,479
Who said anything about breaking up?

329
00:24:37,479 --> 00:24:41,179
I just got impulsive and argued. What are you even saying?

330
00:24:41,179 --> 00:24:44,639
Leave. You came to my house this late to nag me.

331
00:24:44,639 --> 00:24:46,659
I'm going to sleep.

332
00:24:50,459 --> 00:24:53,599
You wouldn't admit your mistake if I didn't provoke you.

333
00:24:54,479 --> 00:24:56,139
Your hand still hasn't healed?

334
00:24:56,139 --> 00:24:58,039
Do you want to see a traditional Chinese medicine doctor?

335
00:24:58,039 --> 00:24:59,724
No need.

336
00:25:12,859 --> 00:25:16,060
What is this stuff? 
    

337
00:25:16,060 --> 00:25:19,240
Is it written with your feet? It's so ugly.

338
00:25:20,199 --> 00:25:25,659
 Xiao Que did nothing wrong. It's my fault. 

339
00:25:33,739 --> 00:25:36,699
 - 45 yuan received.  
 - Please come again.

340
00:25:36,699 --> 00:25:38,384
Okay, goodbye.

341
00:25:41,879 --> 00:25:43,939
Welcome.

342
00:26:01,019 --> 00:26:04,099
- Excuse me. 
 - Order whatever you want yourself.

343
00:26:05,839 --> 00:26:09,879
I want to order something that would make my girlfriend not angry.

344
00:26:09,879 --> 00:26:13,219
Figure it out yourself. We don't have such a thing

345
00:26:13,219 --> 00:26:18,179
that can help inconsiderate, heartless and crabby boyfriends.

346
00:26:18,179 --> 00:26:21,599
So, that's why I brought it myself.

347
00:26:21,599 --> 00:26:25,479
"Seeking Forgiveness" Milk Tea flavor. It's new.

348
00:26:25,479 --> 00:26:26,979
No way.

349
00:26:26,979 --> 00:26:32,439
And "Wanting You Back" Strawberry one. It's new too.

350
00:26:32,439 --> 00:26:34,479
No way.

351
00:26:43,619 --> 00:26:45,699
Then pick one.

352
00:26:46,379 --> 00:26:49,519
With so many flavors, there must be one that's right for you.

353
00:26:49,519 --> 00:26:52,679
Did you buy out that store or what?

354
00:26:52,679 --> 00:26:54,939
If other men make their girlfriends angry,

355
00:26:54,939 --> 00:26:57,899
at least they'd buy them a lipstick.

356
00:26:57,899 --> 00:27:01,679
But you're giving me just lollipops. Are you having financial difficulties?

357
00:27:01,679 --> 00:27:03,779
Actually, no.

358
00:27:03,779 --> 00:27:06,839
It's just that my salary card is with my girlfriend. I can't ask for it.

359
00:27:06,839 --> 00:27:07,959
Get it back.

360
00:27:07,959 --> 00:27:11,079
Things given to a girlfriend must never be asked back.

361
00:27:11,899 --> 00:27:16,399
The love given to a girlfriend can't be taken back even if wanted.

362
00:27:16,399 --> 00:27:19,239
That's so cheesy. Where did you learn that?

363
00:27:19,239 --> 00:27:22,059
I just saw it online.

364
00:27:22,059 --> 00:27:25,159
In the days without me, did you feel you got sloppier?

365
00:27:25,159 --> 00:27:27,019
A total collapse, body and soul.

366
00:27:27,019 --> 00:27:29,939
So I hurried over to fix it.

367
00:27:29,939 --> 00:27:33,539
- Have you recognized your mistake? 
 - Yes, fully.

368
00:27:34,379 --> 00:27:35,679
Didn't cheat?

369
00:27:35,679 --> 00:27:38,999
I'll own up to my mistakes, but I can't accept defamation.

370
00:27:38,999 --> 00:27:41,879
I suppose you wouldn't have the nerve.

371
00:27:41,879 --> 00:27:44,459
You're bold now, arguing and giving me the silent treatment.

372
00:27:44,459 --> 00:27:47,899
- Are you going to break up with me next? 
 - I will never do it.

373
00:27:48,639 --> 00:27:50,819
All right, I'll forgive you since it's your first time.

374
00:27:50,819 --> 00:27:52,899
I give you a reprieve. Prove yourself in the future.

375
00:27:52,899 --> 00:27:55,079
I will mend my ways and start anew.

376
00:27:55,079 --> 00:27:56,799
Today, you do the cleaning.

377
00:27:56,799 --> 00:27:58,359
Yes, Ma'am.

378
00:27:58,359 --> 00:28:00,339
Come closer. Let me have a look.

379
00:28:01,299 --> 00:28:03,699
You've lost weight.

380
00:28:03,699 --> 00:28:05,780
- Have I? 
 - You have.

381
00:28:05,780 --> 00:28:08,460
Let me feel if your abs are still there.

382
00:28:08,460 --> 00:28:11,499
Well, I've lost weight, but my abs are still there.

383
00:28:11,499 --> 00:28:13,859
- Really? Let me feel. 
 - 12 packs.

384
00:28:13,859 --> 00:28:16,339
I'm counting 13 now.

385
00:28:16,959 --> 00:28:18,979
Even an extra one.

386
00:28:34,260 --> 00:28:36,920
Why are you making coffee for me again?

387
00:28:38,339 --> 00:28:41,479
I don't necessarily need this stuff. Don't do it for me again.

388
00:28:41,479 --> 00:28:44,439
Besides, if I want some, I can order delivery.

389
00:28:44,439 --> 00:28:47,839
I'm a VIP at HW Cafe.

390
00:28:47,839 --> 00:28:49,600
I'm not disabled yet.

391
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:53,780
Who said it? I just don't want to drink that much.

392
00:28:55,399 --> 00:28:57,679
I can take care of these things.

393
00:28:57,679 --> 00:29:02,339
Let me make a few more for you while I'm still capable.

394
00:29:04,760 --> 00:29:06,979
   

395
00:29:06,979 --> 00:29:12,299
All right, just add less sugar. I don't want to get diabetes.

396
00:29:12,299 --> 00:29:14,620
I'm too nice to you.

397
00:29:15,759 --> 00:29:17,979
Fine, I'll take it.

398
00:29:22,799 --> 00:29:25,599
It's too sweet. Let's go.

399
00:29:28,999 --> 00:29:31,560
I want to visit my grandfather this weekend.

400
00:29:31,560 --> 00:29:33,799
I'll go back with you.

401
00:29:33,799 --> 00:29:36,979
It's so busy in the shop on weekends. Can you manage to get away?

402
00:29:36,979 --> 00:29:40,799
That's why I'm thinking of hiring another person, but that will cost more.

403
00:29:40,799 --> 00:29:42,979
Although my business is doing okay now,

404
00:29:42,979 --> 00:29:45,939
it'll still take a while to recover the costs.

405
00:29:46,619 --> 00:29:49,239
Take your time. There's no rush.

406
00:29:49,239 --> 00:29:53,439
- Hiring one more person might just bring in more earnings. 
 - Exactly,

407
00:29:53,439 --> 00:29:57,499
if I do hire another one, I might be able to go back with you.

408
00:29:57,499 --> 00:29:59,280
All right.

409
00:29:59,890 --> 00:30:03,710
My grandpa is getting on in years and not in good health.

410
00:30:03,719 --> 00:30:06,439
I'd like to spend more time with him on weekends when I'm free.

411
00:30:06,439 --> 00:30:10,019
Although my parents are with him, they are too busy.

412
00:30:10,019 --> 00:30:12,699
And Xiao Ye is busy with the college entrance examination.

413
00:30:12,699 --> 00:30:14,859
Actually, he is still alone.

414
00:30:14,859 --> 00:30:19,299
How about bringing him over to stay with us?

415
00:30:19,299 --> 00:30:23,739
Okay, I'll go back and ask him this week. If he agrees, I'll bring him over directly.

416
00:30:23,739 --> 00:30:25,839
Sure, I'll tell him on the phone as well.

417
00:30:25,839 --> 00:30:28,100
When you go back, talk to Xiao Ye more.

418
00:30:28,100 --> 00:30:31,053
I feel that he's too repressed being around your parents.

419
00:30:31,053 --> 00:30:34,553
It'd be great if he could really come to Chongqing to study music.

420
00:30:35,899 --> 00:30:40,180
I want to encourage him to study music and do what he likes.

421
00:30:40,180 --> 00:30:42,860
But how do you persuade your parents?

422
00:30:44,360 --> 00:30:50,440
I don't know. Maybe one day they'll understand.

423
00:30:54,079 --> 00:30:55,259
Let's go.

424
00:30:55,259 --> 00:30:56,812
Let's go.

425
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:08,979
- Xiao Tuo. 
 - Grandpa, did you miss me?

426
00:31:11,019 --> 00:31:13,379
And Xiao Que?

427
00:31:13,379 --> 00:31:16,619
She's too busy with the cafe on weekends to come over.

428
00:31:18,199 --> 00:31:20,339
I thought the two of you would come back together.

429
00:31:20,339 --> 00:31:23,159
I have rejoiced too soon.

430
00:31:23,159 --> 00:31:25,539
What do you mean by that?

431
00:31:25,539 --> 00:31:28,079
You don't care about me now, it seems.

432
00:31:28,079 --> 00:31:31,499
You were lying when you said you missed me?

433
00:31:31,499 --> 00:31:35,359
I did miss you, but I also miss Xiao Que.

434
00:31:35,359 --> 00:31:39,559
I'll be happy if both of you are by my side.

435
00:31:40,199 --> 00:31:41,939
Let me help you.

436
00:31:42,779 --> 00:31:45,459
Xiao Que let me tell you to come over to our place.

437
00:31:45,459 --> 00:31:48,419
Stay with us for a few days, just like a vacation.

438
00:31:48,419 --> 00:31:52,099
What vacation? I used to go to your place often.

439
00:31:52,099 --> 00:31:55,459
But now both of us are there, right?

440
00:31:55,459 --> 00:31:58,139
We have a big house over there and you're free.

441
00:31:58,139 --> 00:32:01,159
Just stay for a few days. It won't be a big deal.

442
00:32:01,159 --> 00:32:03,399
But who will water my flowers?

443
00:32:04,779 --> 00:32:07,999
My mom or Xiao Ye can do it, can't they?

444
00:32:07,999 --> 00:32:11,259
Are these flowers more important to you than I am?

445
00:32:11,259 --> 00:32:14,319
I have a gateball match next Monday.

446
00:32:14,319 --> 00:32:15,739
What kind of match is that?

447
00:32:15,739 --> 00:32:19,199
Just grandpas playing gateball. You can play it after you come back.

448
00:32:19,199 --> 00:32:23,159
It's not like that. We are an organized and disciplined team.

449
00:32:23,159 --> 00:32:27,219
Those folks from the University for the Aged are sore losers.

450
00:32:27,219 --> 00:32:28,659
We must beat them.

451
00:32:28,659 --> 00:32:32,799
Let me think about it after I finish the match.

452
00:32:32,799 --> 00:32:35,959
I'll take it as your agreement, okay?

453
00:32:35,959 --> 00:32:38,619
Come over after the match. Call me and I'll pick you up.

454
00:32:38,619 --> 00:32:41,659
No need to pick me up. I can go by myself.

455
00:32:41,659 --> 00:32:43,899
Does your mom know you're here today?

456
00:32:43,899 --> 00:32:47,779
I told her I'd stay with you tonight to let her rest assured.

457
00:32:47,779 --> 00:32:51,199
All right, we will go eat hotpot tonight.

458
00:32:51,199 --> 00:32:53,159
Let's enjoy ourselves.

459
00:32:53,159 --> 00:32:55,744
- I'll go change my shoes. 
 - Okay.

460
