461
00:33:10,559 --> 00:33:12,279
Come in.

462
00:33:15,919 --> 00:33:17,636
Dad.

463
00:33:18,659 --> 00:33:20,779
How come you're here?

464
00:33:22,279 --> 00:33:24,499
I came back to see Grandpa.

465
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:28,419
Does your mom know?

466
00:33:28,419 --> 00:33:30,359
I told her.

467
00:33:30,359 --> 00:33:33,899
She said you were on duty today, so I came to check on you.

468
00:33:41,399 --> 00:33:43,219
You need me?

469
00:33:43,999 --> 00:33:48,359
No. I just haven't been here for a long time.

470
00:33:48,359 --> 00:33:51,619
Has the first floor been renovated?

471
00:33:51,619 --> 00:33:54,179
Yes, it's just been renovated.

472
00:33:54,179 --> 00:33:57,699
They've built a new inpatient department at the back.

473
00:33:57,699 --> 00:34:01,339
Your mom works there now.

474
00:34:05,059 --> 00:34:07,099
Not in the ED? 
  (TN: Emergency Department) 

