00:34:08,199 --> 00:34:12,139
That's good. It is too exhausting in the ED.

476
00:34:20,879 --> 00:34:25,639
Dad, the dining table I designed has already sold a lot.

477
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:27,899
They even gave me a bonus.

478
00:34:30,739 --> 00:34:32,959
It's just a dining table?

479
00:34:33,998 --> 00:34:35,658
Yes.

480
00:34:36,699 --> 00:34:38,678
Your hand?

481
00:34:40,499 --> 00:34:43,159
It's nothing, just a sprain.

482
00:34:48,439 --> 00:34:50,992
Vice Director Lin, consult at bed six.

483
00:34:50,992 --> 00:34:53,512
Okay, I'll go right away.

484
00:35:00,639 --> 00:35:02,559
Go back.

485
00:35:03,839 --> 00:35:06,856
- I'll go pick up Xiao Ye. 
 - Okay.

486
00:35:31,899 --> 00:35:33,839
How come you're back?

487
00:35:33,839 --> 00:35:36,419
Can't I come back to my own home?

488
00:35:36,419 --> 00:35:38,519
Did you come back alone?

489
00:35:39,959 --> 00:35:43,379
Wait, why do all of you ask about Xiao Que as soon as you see me?

